      • from

        public static RejectionEnvelope from(io.spine.core.CommandEnvelope origin,
                                     java.lang.Throwable throwable)
        Creates an instance of Rejection from the rejected command and a Throwable caused by the ThrowableMessage.

        If the producer is not set, uses the RejectionEnvelope.DEFAULT_EVENT_PRODUCER as the producer.

        Parameters:
        origin - the rejected command
        throwable - the caught error
        Returns:
        new instance of Rejection
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the given Throwable is not caused by a ThrowableMessage
